## Import


`aws_ec2_transit_gateway_route_table` can be imported by using the EC2 Transit Gateway Route Table identifier, e.g.

```sh
 $ pulumi import aws:ec2transitgateway/routeTable:RouteTable example tgw-rtb-12345678
```
